data.value:
"English-to-Hindi-Animal-Name-Translator" is an application desgined for children to learn hindi translate of common english animal names. It takes voice input of english animal name and it returns the hindi translation of it.Along with audio output,it also provides picture and text on that animal to make it more attractive.
Created by Mahasin Hossen Munshi and Mayukh Das
